 class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may_la_gi\" title=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Tai_sao_can_su_dung_dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may\" title=\"T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y?\u00a0\">T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y?\u00a0<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Tiep_can_khach_hang_tot_hon\" title=\"Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\">Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Tiep_can_nhieu_khach_hang_cung_luc\" title=\"Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng l\u00fac\">Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng l\u00fac<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Tang_su_chuyen_nghiep_tao_do_than_thien\" title=\"T\u0103ng s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n\">T\u0103ng s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Tang_doanh_so_ban_hang\" title=\"T\u0103ng doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng\">T\u0103ng doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Quy_trinh_dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may_cua_A_Chau_Media_duoc_thuc_hien_nhu_sau\" title=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 sau:\">Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 sau:<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Xay_dung_kich_ban\" title=\"X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Tien_hanh_quay_phim\" title=\"Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh quay phim\">Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh quay phim<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Hau_ki\" title=\"H\u1eadu k\u00ec\">H\u1eadu k\u00ec<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Mot_so_dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may_cua_Achaumedia_cung_cap_toi_khach_hang\" title=\"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Achaumedia cung c\u1ea5p t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Achaumedia cung c\u1ea5p t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/#Tai_sao_ban_nen_lua_chon_dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may_cua_Achaumedia\" title=\"T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Achaumedia?\">T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Achaumedia?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t<em><strong> d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y<\/strong><\/em> th\u00ec d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a\u00a0<strong>Achaumedia<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 uy t\u00edn. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><em><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y<\/strong> <\/em>l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng s\u00fac t\u00edch, \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kinh doanh c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, v\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. M\u1ed9t video ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb 1 \u2013 3 ph\u00fat mang th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13381\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dich-vu-san-xuat-quay-phim-gioi-thieu-dien-may-300x145.jpg\" alt=\"d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t quay phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y\" width=\"850\" height=\"410\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dich-vu-san-xuat-quay-phim-gioi-thieu-dien-may-300x145.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dich-vu-san-xuat-quay-phim-gioi-thieu-dien-may.jpg 760w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi\u00a0nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, \u00e2m thanh s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 kinh doanh c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh doanh nghi\u1ec7p. M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn tr\u1ef1c quan nh\u1ea5t, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111ich th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn n\u01a1i, s\u1edd t\u1eadn tay, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn mua s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/p>\n<p>Th\u00f4ng qua d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 quay phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 pr qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c marketing hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, \u0111ang thay th\u1ebf cho c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c PR, Marketing truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 mang th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng qua nh\u1eefng video<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam:<a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-cong-nghe.html\/\">\u00a0<em><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_sao_can_su_dung_dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y?\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13383\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may-300x145.png\" alt=\"gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y\" width=\"850\" height=\"410\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may-300x145.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.png 760w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tiep_can_khach_hang_tot_hon\"><\/span><strong>Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u00f4ng qua h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c quay video th\u1eddi trang. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Do th\u1eddi gian b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ea3nh r\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Zalo, Facebook,\u2026\u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm v\u00e0 mua b\u00e1n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.<\/p>\n<p>Do \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quay 1 video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 trang web c\u00f4ng ty. \u0110\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd th\u00f4ng qua chatbox, email v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i hay comment.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tiep_can_nhieu_khach_hang_cung_luc\"><\/span><span id=\"Tiep_can_nhieu_khach_hang_cung_luc\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng l\u00fac<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c\u00a0<strong>quay phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y. <\/strong>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u00ec h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00f9ng trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng nhau.<\/p>\n<p>Chi ph\u00ed v\u1eabn v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem t\u0103ng l\u00ean th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, vi\u1ec7c chia s\u1ebb qua m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tang_su_chuyen_nghiep_tao_do_than_thien\"><\/span><span id=\"Tang_su_chuyen_nghiep,_tao_do_than_thien\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>T\u0103ng s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p hay c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng th\u1eddi trang th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u1eb1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi h\u1ecd quay video qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o th\u1eddi trang. T\u1eeb c\u00e1ch b\u00e0i tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng gian cho \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, khi quay video qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o th\u1eddi trang\u00a0th\u00ec nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u1eaft m\u1eaft v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch c\u0169ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u01a1n. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tang_doanh_so_ban_hang\"><\/span><strong>T\u0103ng doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sau khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c quay phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u1eddi trang, l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u0169ng cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c c\u0169.<\/p>\n<p>Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem t\u0103ng l\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Khi quay s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, m\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 trang ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb9p trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc ti\u1ec1n b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u01b0a th\u00edch cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam:\u00a0<em><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-video-gioi-thieu-my-pham.html\/\">S\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/a><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may_cua_A_Chau_Media_duoc_thuc_hien_nhu_sau\"><\/span><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 sau:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u1edbc phim qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng quy tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi cao. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13384\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dien-may-xanh-300x198.jpg\" alt=\"\u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y xanh\" width=\"850\" height=\"561\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dien-may-xanh-300x198.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dien-may-xanh.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Xay_dung_kich_ban\"><\/span><span id=\"Xay_dung_kich_ban\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Theo nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p hay m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh. Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng so \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t cao. K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 khung s\u01b0\u1eddn cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u1edbc phim.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tien_hanh_quay_phim\"><\/span><span id=\"Tien_hanh_quay_phim\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh quay phim<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>T\u1eeb k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n c\u00e0ng chi ti\u1ebft th\u00ec c\u1ea3nh quay c\u00e0ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ea1o c\u1ee5, phong c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m quay\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 quay phim s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y g\u00f3c v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hau_ki\"><\/span><span id=\"Hau_ki\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>H\u1eadu k\u00ec<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sau khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh d\u00e0n d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 quay phim, h\u1eadu k\u00ec l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u1eaft gh\u00e9p, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea3nh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. \u0110\u1ec3 cho ra s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m video ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m h\u1eadu k\u00ec c\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u00e2m thanh.<\/p>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o doanh nghi\u1ec7p cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c, l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 quy m\u00f4\u2026 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Do \u0111\u00f3, thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n kh\u00f4 khan th\u00ec th\u01b0\u1edbc phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ec3 phim qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u1edf n\u00ean sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n h\u1eadu k\u00ec s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng b\u1eb1ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p.<\/li>\n<li>T\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng deadline, giao s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n.<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ghi h\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u00e1p \u1ee9ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ch\u1ec9 sau 2 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda.<\/li>\n<li>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u00fd thu th\u00eam ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-quay-phim-gioi-thieu-doanh-nghiep-tai-da-nang.html\/\"><em><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 quay phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u doanh nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mot_so_dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may_cua_Achaumedia_cung_cap_toi_khach_hang\"><\/span><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Achaumedia cung c\u1ea5p t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>V\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n nay, nhu c\u1ea7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c g\u00f3i d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 t\u00ean m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u00f3i d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay nh\u01b0:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>S\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u doanh nghi\u1ec7p (Phim t\u1ef1 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u doanh nghi\u1ec7p)<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t TVC qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, viral video\u2026<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim ng\u1eafn theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim ph\u00f3ng s\u1ef1<\/li>\n<li>Video h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p\u2026<\/li>\n<li>Quay phim ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o, h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb, GALA, party<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/san-xuat-clip-quang-cao-san-phan-nha-o-van-phong.html\/\"><em><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t clip qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m nh\u00e0 \u1edf, v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng ty \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0:<\/strong><em> si\u00eau th\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y xanh, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y PICO, Media Mart, <\/em><em>C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n X\u00e2y L\u1eafp K\u1ef9 Thu\u1eadt C.H.K, <\/em><em>\u0110i\u1ec7n L\u1ea1nh Hi\u1ec7p Anh Nh\u1ea5t &#8211; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i &#8211; D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 &#8211; K\u1ef9 Thu\u1eadt Hi\u1ec7p Anh Nh\u1ea5t, <\/em><em>C\u01a1 \u0110i\u1ec7n L\u1ea1nh Fornax &#8211; C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n C\u01a1 \u0110i\u1ec7n L\u1ea1nh Fornax Vi\u1ec7t Nam,<\/em> <em>C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ea7u T\u01b0 V\u00e0 Ph\u00e1t Tri\u1ec3n K\u1ef9 Thu\u1eadt Ti\u1ebfn M\u1ea1nh,<\/em><em>\u0110i\u1ec7n L\u1ea1nh Minh Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ph\u00fac &#8211; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 \u0110i\u1ec7n L\u1ea1nh Minh Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ph\u00fac, <\/em><em>\u0110i\u1ec7n L\u1ea1nh Ph\u00fa M\u1ef9 &#8211; C\u00f4ng TY TNHH \u0110i\u1ec7n L\u1ea1nh S\u1ea1ch,&#8230;.\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_sao_ban_nen_lua_chon_dich_vu_san_xuat_phim_gioi_thieu_san_pham_dien_may_cua_Achaumedia\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Achaumedia?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13389 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/achaumedia-2-12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/achaumedia-2-12.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/achaumedia-2-12-300x176.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/achaumedia-2-12-768x452.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p:<\/strong>\u00a0C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 vi\u00ean nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, m\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi, gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng project \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n, \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i:<\/strong>\u00a0Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb, c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u1edbc phim ch\u00e2n th\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u1ea1nh tranh, h\u1ee3p l\u00fd:<\/strong>\u00a0T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 chi ph\u00ed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4ng khai, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 r\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111a s\u1ed1 doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li><strong>\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng:<\/strong>\u00a0Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ea1n khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c k\u00ed k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai b\u00ean lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 nguy\u1ec7n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng deadline th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 tin c\u1eady, uy t\u00edn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Lu\u00f4n l\u1eafng nghe, lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5u hi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3\u00a0<em><strong>d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y<\/strong><\/em>, h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay v\u1edbi Achaumedia \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y th\u00ec d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a\u00a0Achaumedia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 uy t\u00edn. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y nh\u00e9! D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13392,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[64,63,39,41,42],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y th\u00ec d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a\u00a0Achaumedia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 uy t\u00edn.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-san-xuat-phim-gioi-thieu-san-pham-dien-may.html\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\